    "description": {
      "value": "<p>This staff has 10 charges and regains [[/r 1d6 + 4]] expended charges daily at dawn. If you expend the last charge, roll a d20. On a 1, a swarm of insects consumes and destroys the staff, then disperses. The staff has the following additional properties:</p><p><em><strong>Spells.</strong></em> While holding the staff, you can use an action to expend some of its charges to cast one of the following spells from it, using your spell save DC: <em>@UUID[Compendium.black-flag.spells.Item.7irCOXrPAuMjPYJH]{giant insect}</em> (4 charges) or <em>@UUID[Compendium.black-flag.spells.Item.lGmxkutPlXsgyzRd]{insect plague}</em> (5 charges).</p><p><em><strong>Insect Cloud.</strong></em> While holding the staff, you can use an action and expend 1 charge to cause a swarm of harmless flying insects to spread out in a 30â€‘foot radius from you. The insects remain for 10 minutes, making the area heavily obscured for creatures other than you. The swarm moves with you, remaining centered on you. A wind of at least 10 miles per hour disperses the swarm and ends the effect.</p>",
